      "title": "Oil queue in Bambalapitiya to Kollupitiya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Queues of vehicles to get fuel have been covering Kollupitiya and Bambalapitiya areas since this (7) morning.",
        "Bambalapitiya I.O.C. To get fuel from the filling station, vehicles were stretched along the coastal road from Kerepupitiya to Galle Road. The photo shows a queue of tricycles on the coastal road."
      ],
